
Cluster Architecture
 ├── Control Plane
 │    ├─ High-availability (multi-master)
 │    ├─ Etcd clustering & backup
 │    ├─ API server scaling
 │    └─ Scheduler optimization
 │
 ├── Worker Nodes
 │    ├─ Node sizing (CPU, memory, GPU if needed)
 │    ├─ Node autoscaling (Cluster Autoscaler)
 │    ├─ OS tuning (kernel, cgroups, sysctl)
 │    └─ Resource isolation (taints & tolerations)
 │
 ├── Multi-Cluster / Hybrid
 │    ├─ Federation or cluster API
 │    ├─ Edge & cloud integration
 │    └─ Cluster segmentation for latency / fault isolation

Compute & Workload
 ├─ CPU / Memory / GPU allocation
 ├─ Vertical Pod Autoscaler (VPA)
 ├─ Horizontal Pod Autoscaler (HPA)
 ├─ Pod resource requests & limits
 ├─ QoS classes (Guaranteed / Burstable / BestEffort)
 ├─ Node affinity & anti-affinity
 └─ Workload isolation with namespaces & network policies

Networking
 ├─ CNI choice (Calico, Cilium, Flannel, Weave)
 ├─ Network policies for isolation & security
 ├─ Load balancing (Service type: ClusterIP, NodePort, LoadBalancer)
 ├─ Ingress controllers & API gateway
 ├─ Service mesh (Istio, Linkerd) for observability / traffic management
 └─ DNS & service discovery optimization


Storage
 ├─ Persistent Volumes (PV) & Persistent Volume Claims (PVC)
 ├─ Storage Classes & dynamic provisioning
 ├─ High-performance storage (Ceph, Portworx, Longhorn, NVMe drives)
 ├─ Backup & restore strategies
 └─ StatefulSets for databases / queues

Observability
 ├─ Metrics (Prometheus + Node/Pod exporters)
 ├─ Logging (ELK/EFK stack, Loki)
 ├─ Tracing (Jaeger, OpenTelemetry)
 ├─ Alerts & notifications (Alertmanager, PagerDuty, Slack)
 └─ Dashboards (Grafana, K8s Dashboard)

Security
 ├─ RBAC & service accounts
 ├─ Pod Security Standards / Policies
 ├─ Secrets management (K8s Secrets, HashiCorp Vault)
 ├─ Network segmentation (network policies)
 ├─ Image scanning & admission controllers
 └─ TLS / mTLS for services


CI/CD & GitOps
 ├─ GitOps tooling (Argo CD, Flux)
 ├─ Automated deployment pipelines
 ├─ Progressive delivery (canary, blue-green)
 ├─ Rollbacks & versioned manifests
 └─ Integration with CI tools (GitLab CI, Jenkins, Tekton)


Performance & Reliability
 ├─ Node & Pod auto-scaling
 ├─ Cluster autoscaler & over-provisioning
 ├─ Resource & quota management
 ├─ High availability & failover strategies
 ├─ Load testing & benchmarking
 └─ QoS for latency-sensitive workloads

Backup & DR
 ├─ Etcd backups & restores
 ├─ Application-level backups (databases, PVs)
 ├─ Cluster snapshots
 ├─ Multi-region / multi-AZ replication
 └─ Rolling upgrades & zero-downtime patching

Automation
 ├─ Helm charts & Kustomize for templating
 ├─ Operators for databases / messaging systems
 ├─ Infrastructure as Code (Terraform, Crossplane)
 ├─ Policy enforcement (OPA/Gatekeeper)
 └─ Auto-remediation (Argo Events, K8s controllers)
